#: src/event-list.c:1307
msgid ""
"Show only the <b>first occurrence</b> of repeating events.\n"
"By default, all occurrences are shown.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Note:</b>\n"
"- Urgencies are still shown for all events.\n"
"- Repeating events may appear earlier in the list because only the first occurrence is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Toon uitsluitend de <b>eerste gebeurtenis</b> van herhalende gebeurtenissen.\n"
"Standaard worden alle gebeurtenissen getoond.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Let op:</b>\n"
"- Urgenties worden nog steeds voor alle gebeurtenissen getoond.\n"
"- Herhalende gebeurtenissen kunnen eerder in de lijst verschijnen wanneer alleen de eerste gebeurtenis wordt getoond."

#: src/event-list.c:1319
msgid "also old"
msgstr "ook oude"

#: src/event-list.c:1325
msgid ""
"Show old events in the list.\n"
"\n"
"This option is only available when <b>Only first repeating</b> is enabled to avoid very long lists.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Note:</b> The extra days setting still controls how many future appointments are shown."
msgstr ""
"Toon oude gebeurtenissen in de lijst.\n"
"\n"
"Deze optie is alleen beschikbaar wanneer <b>Alleen eerste herhalend</b> is ingeschakeld om zeer lange lijsten te vermijden.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Let op:</b> De extra-dagen-instelling bepaalt nog steeds hoeveel toekomstige afspraken er worden getoond."

