#: src/event-list.c:1499
msgid ""
"Double click line to edit it.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Flags in order:</b>\n"
"1. Alarm:\n"
"   n = no alarm, A = alarm is set, P = persistent alarm is set\n"
"2. Recurrence:\n"
"   n = no recurrence, H = hourly, D = daily, W = weekly, M = monthly, Y = yearly\n"
"3. Type:\n"
"   f = free, B = busy\n"
"4. Located in file:\n"
"   O = Orage, A = archive, F = foreign\n"
"5. Appointment type:\n"
"   E = event, T = todo, J = journal"
msgstr ""
"Dubbelklik op een regel om hem te bewerken.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Vlaggen op volgorde:</b>\n"
"1. Alarm:\n"
"   n = geen alarm, A = alarm is ingesteld, P = blijvend alarm is ingesteld\n"
"2. Herhaling:\n"
"   n = geen herhalingen, H = uurlijks, D = dagelijks, W = wekelijks, M = maandelijks, Y = jaarlijks\n"
"3. Type:\n"
"   f = beschikbaar, B = bezig\n"
"4. Aangetroffen in bestand:\n"
"   O = Orage, A = archief, F = vreemd\n"
"5. Afspraaktype:\n"
"   E = gebeurtenis, T = taak, J = dagboek"

